  Sagittarius

There is a rapid fluster of activity around you today that you should latch onto, dear Sagittarius. You will find yourself on a magic carpet ride that takes you into the clouds. The most difficult thing to remember, however, is to not get so carried away that you lose sight of the ground. Keep in mind that reality isn't always exactly the way it seems. What seems to be working perfectly today may not work at all tomorrow.
